How many days the access logs should be present in the file

Log Retention (Important for Compliance) : By default, Jira does not rotate or delete access logs automatically.

Configure the log retention
•	Create a logrotate config
•	sudo vi /etc/logrotate.d/jira-access
/opt/atlassian/jira/logs/jira_access_log*.log {
    daily
    rotate 90		#this is retaining for 90days
    compress
    missingok
    notifempty
    copytruncate
}
•	Now to save the VI editor file press escape
•	Now type :wq and press enter
